{"word":"Ear","slug":"ear","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Ear</b> Blood put upon:<br/> - In consecration of priests<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=29&verse=20'>Exo 29:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=8&verse=23'>Lev 8:23</a> <br/> - In cleansing lepers<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=14&verse=14'>Lev 14:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=14&verse=25'>Lev 14:25</a> <br/> Anointed with oil in purifications<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=14&verse=17'>Lev 14:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=14&verse=28'>Lev 14:28</a><br/> Bored as a sign of servitude<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=21&verse=6'>Exo 21:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=40&verse=6'>Psa 40:6</a><br/><a href='S:Deafness'>Deafness</a><br/> Figurative, anthropomorphic uses of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=17&verse=6'>Psa 17:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=39&verse=12'>Psa 39:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=77&verse=1'>Psa 77:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=80&verse=1'>Psa 80:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=84&verse=8'>Psa 84:8</a>"}]}